    <text>
        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>The Hague</placeName>&#44; <date>August 1&#44; 1853</date>.</p>
			<p>To the Reverend</p>
			<p>Sir <addressee>I. Leeser</addressee>&#44;</p>
			<p>at <placeName>P<hi rend="underline">hila</hi>delphia</placeName>.</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Some months ago I had the<lb/> honour to forward to you some<lb/> literary productions in answer to<lb/> your very cheering letter I did receive<lb/> some times before. I hope the<lb/> said publications have been duly received<lb/> by you.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">These few lines are destined<lb/> to recommend to your benevolent<lb/> attention <persName>M. B. D&#39;Ancona de Sear<add>&#63;</add></persName>&#44;<lb/> Dutchman&#44; of a very respectable family&#44;<lb/> and an <sic>irreprocheable</sic> character&#44; himself&#44;<lb/> who&#44; by revertes of fortune&#44; has been<lb/> driven to the new world&#44; <add>&#63;</add> the research<lb/> for him and his numerous family of the<lb/> necessary means of existence.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Will be so kind to lend him the<lb/> support you may dispose of&#58; <persName>M. d&#39;Ancona</persName><lb/> deserves it&#44; by his conduct and relations.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Believe me&#44; Sir&#44; truly your</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">most humble servant&#44; <persName role="author">J H Belinfante</persName></p>
		<pb n="2"/>
          <p rend="indent(1)">To</p>
			<p>the <addressee>Reverend Sir I. Leeser</addressee>&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Jewish minister</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">at</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi></placeName></p>
		<pb n="Envelope"/>
			<p><hi rend="underline">Rev</hi>.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi></placeName></p>
          
        </body>
